<TITLE> Madrasas, secondary schools open on Feb 21, Mar 26 and Dec 16 </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, May 12 (bdnews24.com)Madrasas along with secondary schools will remain open on Feb 21, Mar 26 and Dec 16the national holidays, the education minister said on Tuesday. The ministry in an order also announced the decision to make school students understand the significance of the days. But there will be no classes and examinations on these days, the circular said. Nurul Islam Nahid, the minister, he told reporters at a programme at the National Academy for Education Management auditorium that the earlier decision that ordered these schools shut on those days has been changed. Asked if colleges and universities would also remain open he said there was no need for that. Many programmes are held to mark these days in colleges and universities, he explained
